Junior password

Password has 6-8 characters
Password only contains lower case letters and numbers
Of course, the first 3 characters have to be "jr-" to denote a junior passoword

How many different passwords are there?


Password has 8-10 characters
Password only contains letters (upper and lower), and numbers
The password must have three consecutive characters in at least one place
The sum of all the numbers in the password can't be greater than it's length

How many different passwords are there?